title: 316 - Best of 2021
description:
In this episode, the guys share nuggets and laughter from 2021, the year that was.


4:00 - "Don't use your technique and form when you're tired. Work on your endurance."- Jemal 

10:00 - "Run the play that was called in your life. Whether in business or sports. Stick to the plan."- Jemal

12:00 - "Don't let your pride stop you from asking for help."- ET
